OL,3,CStore owner with 'worst rat
OL,4,Cinfestation ever seen' fined almost
OL,5,C#30,000
OL,7,FThe owner of a grocery store in
OL,8,FSwindon, which had the "worst rat
OL,9,Finfestation ever seen" by a council
OL,10,Finspector, has been fined almost
OL,11,F#30,000.
OL,13,FStaff from Swindon Borough Council
OL,14,Fvisited India Bazzar on Broad Street
OL,15,Fin Broadgreen in November 2023.
OL,17,FOne environmental health inspector
OL,18,Fdescribed it as the worst rat
OL,19,Finfestation she had seen in her 24-
OL,20,Fyear career.
