OL,4,Cinfestation ever seen' fined almost
OL,5,C#30,000
OL,7,FCouncil officers visited the store
OL,8,Fwhen it was open and serving customers.
OL,10,FThe immediately noticed large
OL,11,Fquantities of rat droppings on the
OL,12,Ffloor, and on shelving.
OL,14,FLarge amounts of food items, including
OL,15,Fready-to-eat foods such as biscuits,
OL,16,Fpastries, salt and peanuts had also
OL,17,Fbeen gnawed by the rodents.
