OL,3,CStore owner with 'worst rat
OL,4,Cinfestation ever seen' fined almost
OL,5,C#30,000
OL,7,FA bag of flour was found on display,
OL,8,Fwhich was stained with rat urine.
OL,9,FThere were smear marks seen all over
OL,10,Fthe walls and on food packaging.
OL,12,FThere was a strong musty smell of rat
OL,13,Furine in the shop which was described
OL,14,Fby the food hygiene officer as
OL,15,F"overpowering", with gnawed electrical
OL,16,Fcables above shelving units.
OL,18,FThere was also evidence of gnawed bags
OL,19,Fof food being taped over and placed
OL,20,Fback on the shelves for sale.
