OL,4,Cinfestation ever seen' fined almost
OL,5,C#30,000
OL,7,FAs there were clear signs of an
OL,8,Finfestation, officers served a Hygiene
OL,9,FEmergency Prohibition Notice,
OL,10,Fimmediately closing the business for
OL,11,Fsix weeks.
OL,13,FThe court heard how there was no pest
OL,14,Fcontrol contract in place and that Mr
OL,15,FMuthu Kumaravelu was self-treating the
OL,16,Finfestation with grain bait and bait
OL,17,Fblocks placed in white bowls around
OL,18,Fthe shop.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
