OL,3,CStore owner with 'worst rat
OL,4,Cinfestation ever seen' fined almost
OL,5,C#30,000
OL,7,FHe informed council officers he was
OL,8,Fblocking holes in walls and doors with
OL,9,Ffishing net, which he acknowledged was
OL,10,Fineffective, as the rats were gnawing
OL,11,Faround it.
OL,13,FOn 11th December 2023 following
OL,14,Fimprovements made by Mr Kumaravelu,
OL,15,Fcouncil officers allowed the business
OL,16,Fto reopen.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
