OL,4,Cinfestation ever seen' fined almost
OL,5,C#30,000
OL,7,FDuring the investigation, Mr
OL,8,FKumaravelu, under caution, denied
OL,9,Fthere was an active infestation,
OL,10,Fstating there were only a few packages
OL,11,Fthat were damaged and only four to
OL,12,Ffive items found by officers. He also
OL,13,Fblamed staff for not disposing of
OL,14,Fgnawed food and for taping up products.
OL,16,FSimon Kiely, prosecuting for Swindon
OL,17,FBorough Council, said: "It took six
OL,18,Fweeks and several visits for the
OL,19,Fproperty to be ready to re-open with
OL,20,Fthe same advice given over and over.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
