OL,3,CStore owner with 'worst rat
OL,4,Cinfestation ever seen' fined almost
OL,5,C#30,000
OL,7,F"It is clear that Mr Kumaravelu, both
OL,8,Fon his own behalf and on behalf of the
OL,9,Fbusiness, was clearly and evidently
OL,10,Faware of the extensive rat infestation
OL,11,Fat the premises on and prior to 2
OL,12,FNovember 2023, but had failed to take
OL,13,Fsufficient steps to address the
OL,14,Finfestation until the prosecuting
OL,15,Fauthority's intervention."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
