OL,3,CStore owner with 'worst rat
OL,4,Cinfestation ever seen' fined almost
OL,5,C#30,000
OL,7,FJohn Bishop, representing India Bazzar
OL,8,F(PVT) Ltd and Mr Kumaravelu, told the
OL,9,Fcourt that a lack of funds were at the
OL,10,Froot of the problem and that his
OL,11,Fclient had gone to considerable
OL,12,Flengths to remedy the issues, adding
OL,13,Fthat he had learned a very hard lesson.
OL,15,FMagistrates fined Mr Kumaravelu
OL,16,F#20,000 and also ordered him to pay
OL,17,Ffull prosecution costs of #6,479, as
OL,18,Fwell as a victim surcharge of #2,000.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
