OL,4,Cinfestation ever seen' fined almost
OL,5,C#30,000
OL,7,FHis business was fined #500, plus a
OL,8,Fvictim surcharge of #200. In total, Mr
OL,9,FKumaravelu owed the Court #29,179.
OL,11,FFollowing the hearing, Councillor Jim
OL,12,FGrant, Swindon Borough Council's
OL,13,FCabinet Member for Communities and
OL,14,FPartnerships, said: "Our Environmental
OL,15,FHealth Officers found appalling
OL,16,Fconditions at this premises, as
OL,17,Fconfirmed by the court, and took
OL,18,Fdecisive action to protect the health
OL,19,Fof Swindon residents.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
