OL,7,F"We are pleased the court imposed such
OL,8,Fa significant sentence. I hope it
OL,9,Fsends a strong message that food
OL,10,Fhygiene needs to be taken extremely
OL,11,Fseriously.
OL,13,F"Food business operators should ensure
OL,14,Ftheir premises are protected from the
OL,15,Fimpact of pests at all times, as
OL,16,Finfestations can quickly escalate, and
OL,17,Fpresent significant risks to both
OL,18,Ftheir customers and their business."
